 of sportsmanship and have a chance to get to the Olympics will never be able to do so because they were killed by Russia.1 / 10      Several city councillors and representatives of the Paris City Hall took part in the action.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999817199767, \"rank\": 1.8280021313593944e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9878804291275387, \"rank\": 0.01226822896048765, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991164259, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris City Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The participants also mentioned Russian and Belarusian athletes who, although under a neutral flag, will still participate in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9612359700319408, \"rank\": 0.03910454015737267, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9998300618150913, \"rank\": 0.0001697539078626434, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbped